extends /components/layout.pug

block title
    title Academy of Learning | Home

block content 
    .container-fluid
        .row 
            include ./indexsections/header.pug
        .row
            include ./indexsections/row1.pug
        .row 


           p.text-center
            a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.orange-btn(href='aboutus.html' role='button') ABOUT AOLCC
        .row
              .col-lg-12.mb-4.mt-2.text-center
                    h2 FEATURES
            .container-fluid
                .row
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 LEARN AT YOUR OWN PACE
                        p Our campuses provide a relaxing atmosphere where you can learn at your own pace. The features of our Integrated Learning System&reg; allow for flexibility in your daily schedule. You can finish your program quickly to get into the job market faster.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 JOB PLACEMENT
                        p Diploma programs feature real-world job placement so you&apos;re job-ready at graduation. A number of our adult learners are hired by their placement sites.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 PRACTICAL EXPERIENCE
                        p Many of our programs feature a practical component in which learners gain valuable experience with actual clients.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 SHORT, EFFECTIVE COURSES
                        p We offer short programs, so you can earn your Diploma or Certificate in just 4-12 months instead of the conventional 2-4 years at a Community College or University. This gives you the financial flexibility to get into the workforce sooner, instead of being tied to a Community College or University for several years.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 FLEXIBLE SCHEDULING
                        p Work / Life balance is important. Don&apos;t give up on your dream of a better career to help you and your family. Our flexible hours and online learning allow you to earn a Diploma or Certificate with minimal disruption to your daily schedule.
                        | You&apos;ll be able to balance your education with your employment and your family. With our continuous enrolment, it is never too late for you to start.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 DIPLOMA AND CERTIFICATE PROGRAMS
                        p We offer over 30 Diploma and Certificate programs for you to choose from. For one-on-one support, Learning Coaches are available at all times to provide personalized guidance and assistance to help you succeed!
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 HANDS-ON TRAINING
                        p Audio, visual, online and rich media instructions are used to explain concepts and guide learners through initial skill-based applications. Hands-on tasks give students an opportunity to apply skills to &ldquo;real life&rdquo; situations. We help you master the subject matter before moving onto the next lesson.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 SAFE, COMFORTABLE LEARNING ENVIRONMENT
                        p There&apos;s no intimidating classroom atmosphere or competition! We ensure a comfortable, safe and friendly learning environment for all adult learners. If you need to miss a lesson, you can take the same lesson at another time. With ILS&reg; and online learning you&apos;ll never miss an assignment or lesson.
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6.col-sm-12.text-center
                        h3 INTEGRATED LEARNING SYSTEM (ILS&reg;)
                        p Course materials and instructions provide an all-encompassing learning experience using multi-sensory learning styles and preferences through student workbooks, media presentations, and hands-on activities.
            .container-fluid
                .row
                    .text-center.col-md-8.col-12.mx-auto
                        h1.orange-text DEDICATED TO QUALITY
                        p Our programs are conceived and developed with learners&apos; needs and ease of use in mind. At Academy of Learning Career College, Canada&apos;s largest career college network, our training program will set you up for success. Learn more about our world-class Integrated Learning System (ILS&reg;).
                    .position-images.wpb_single_image.center
                        img(alt='Academy of Learning Integrated Learning System' src='/images/ils.webp')
                    .orange.text-center.banner
                        a.white-text-md(href='programs/') We have more than 30+ programs. EXPLORE &gt;
                    .banner(style='height: 10px;')
                        .inline-block
                            .sixtypcthz
                                img.sixtypcthz(alt='Map of Campuses on an iMac' src='/images/imac-final.webp')
                            .fiftypcthz.float-right
                                h1 50+ CAMPUSES ACROSS CANADA.
                                h2 As a Canadian Owned and Operated Company, we are proud to deliver quality Education to our fellow Canadians.
                                hr
                                p With 50+ campuses across Canada we are Canada&apos;s largest career college. As a Canadian owned and operated company, we understand the requirements of Canadian learners and tailor our curriculum and learning outcomes for the realities of the Canadian job market.
                        .btn 
                            a(href='locations/') FIND A LOCATION NEAR YOU
                        .grey-bg.text-center.white-text
                            p CALL US TODAY AT 604-855-3315
                            p WE STRIVE TO PROVIDE OUR ADULT LEARNERS WITH THE HIGHEST QUALITY IN EDUCATION, CURRICULUM, SERVICE AND TECHNOLOGY
                .row
                    .col-sm-4.col-auto.mx-auto
                        a.btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-success.orange-btn(href='ils.html' title='') LEARN MORE
                .row.afulliframe
                    .row.text-center
                        h2 Request more info
                .row.text-center
                    iframe.moreinfoform(title='moreinfoform' src='//form1.campuslogin.com/Academy_of_Learning_College/10400/Lead/AbbotsfordLangley.campuslogin?&style=//aolccbc.com/forms/clform.css')
